Author: brix-and-mortar
Text: Get rid of the apps. They exacerbated my eating disorder 10 fold. Kudos to not binging though.  I always think how when I stop a binge and throw the food out it’s slashing future medical costs from my purges.  So it’s not entirely wasteful.

Author: livipup
Text: This post made me realize that I never installed Door Dash even though I was going to and now that I have I feel like it was a mistake. Nothing is open at this hour, but just looking at all the options that aren't on other apps made me start feeling hungry.
